{{flavour|This rod allows its wielder to smite foes from afar.}}

The '''rod of smiting''' can be evoked to smite any enemy within your [[LOS]], with the attack treated as a level 4 [[Smiting]] spell. Although its damage output is not too impressive, it can hit enemies hiding behind their allies and is useful for taking down fleeing monsters.

{{crawlquote|Damage <nowiki>=</nowiki> 7 + 33 * (1d(5 + 3 * Evocations) - 1)/191}}

==History==
Rods of smiting were removed in [[0.11]].

